    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Fireworks for SWKS]]></title>
    <link href="http://www.thetatrades.com/blog/2017/02/16/fireworks-for-swks/"/>
    <updated>2017-02-16T22:07:45-08:00</updated>
    <id>http://www.thetatrades.com/blog/2017/02/16/fireworks-for-swks</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hey traders,</p>

<p>We particularly like to look for stocks that are currently consolidating with a potential of moving higher with the trend of the market. One particular candidate to put on our watchlist is $SWKS. Please observe the chart below</p>

<p><a href="/images/blog/20170216/swks.png"><img src="/images/blog/20170216/swks.png" alt="$SWKS - 2017-02-16 - Daily" /></a></p>

<p>$SWKS has exploded like a firework after earnings and has recently consolidated around the 92 level. As the 20MA catches up, we&rsquo;re looking for buyers to step in and hold price above that curve. We&rsquo;re looking for another set of fireworks - a breakout above 94. It wouldn&rsquo;t be a bad idea to start accumulating some long deltas. For stock, we&rsquo;ll be going long at 91.80 with a stop below the 20MA at 87.46.</p>

