    <id>http://www.thetatrades.com/blog/2017/02/13/whooping</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>We love looking for consolidation patterns and trading with the trend. One particular candidate that fits these criteria is $COF. Please observe the chart below.</p>

<h3 id="20170213-cof">$COF</h3>


<p><a href="/images/blog/20170213/cof.png"><img src="/images/blog/20170213/cof.png" alt="$COF - 2017-02-13 - Daily" /></a></p>

<p>$COF has been consolidating after a huge move to the upside. With the recent breakout in the financials ETF $XLF, we&rsquo;re looking for continued upside. We&rsquo;ll look to get long at a break above yesterday&rsquo;s high: 89.59. Our stop loss will be a close below 85.24, as we&rsquo;re expecting the 50MA to hold, but giving ourself some room for noise. And as long as trend holds, we continue holding this long.</p>

